  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual color blast puzzler - Cube Blast will challenge even the most reputable puzzle solvers with a mind bending 3D twist on the classic color blast formula. Push your spatial thinking abilities by solving increasingly complex puzzles on a 3D tower of colorful blocks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a casual player or part of the hardcore puzzle solver crowd, Cube Blast will keep you entertained. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452870/extras/f3fad302fa3d30b0b4f42d655b620822.poster.avif?t=1740118327\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452870/extras/f3fad302fa3d30b0b4f42d655b620822.webm?t=1740118327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452870/extras/f3fad302fa3d30b0b4f42d655b620822.mp4?t=1740118327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Think in 3 dimensions!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A diverse range  mechanics will keep you engaged level by level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452870/extras/6394a8367d91e10bb17896d170e12fc9.poster.avif?t=1740118327\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452870/extras/6394a8367d91e10bb17896d170e12fc9.webm?t=1740118327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/452870/extras/6394a8367d91e10bb17896d170e12fc9.mp4?t=1740118327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> <br>Satisfying booms</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual, vibrant, snappy aesthetic strengthened by satisfying explosions rewards each solved puzzle, while cute aliens guide you through their world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
